# Version
$ ruby -v
ruby 2.0.0p353 (2013-11-22 revision 43784) [x86_64-linux]

# Run the MVC example
$ ./mvcpatterndemo.rb

##############################################################################
This ruby program is based on the Model-View-Controller (MVC) pattern java
example at http://www.tutorialspoint.com/design_pattern/mvc_pattern.htm

The intention is to give a very simple MVC example from first principles
(without using a web framework or other framework library).

